itle=郭冠英事件的真相是什麼？|url=https://www.coolloud.org.tw/node/36829|accessdate=|author=石之瑜|date=2009-03-17|format=|publisher=中國時報(苦勞網轉載)|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715105937/https://www.coolloud.org.tw/node/36829|dead-url=no}}</ref>

